   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,512:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |------|------|------|
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,514:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,515:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,515:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ConsultAgent
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,516:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,516:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: consult_agent.py
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,517:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | 单个专家智能体，含4阶段方法 |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,517:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,518:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,518:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ConsultationPipeline
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,519:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,520:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: consultation.py
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,520:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | 流程编排与报告综合 |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,521:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,522:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,522:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: build_clone_prompt
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,523:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | 
