   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,524:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Level 2 知识档案注入 |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,524:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-12 14:34:12,525:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 专家面板 | 
